  "text": "The structure was solved by molecular replacement using MOLREP [CITATION_1] and the coordinates of human CN (PDB entry 1AUI) as search model. Refinement was performed with REFMAC5 [CITATION_2] and the molecular-graphics program COOT [CITATION_3] (Table 1) . Non-crystallographic restraints together with the restraints of the trans-CNA subunit towards high resolution information were also applied.",
